Package lab3

Class LeagueTest

java.lang.Object
lab3.LeagueTest
public class LeagueTest extends Object
JUnit test class for the Fantasy Sports League Management System. Tests are ordered by method name for consistent execution. ScoringFormat constructors are private - only static factory methods are tested.
Since:
Fall 2025
Author:
Dr. Sukhwant Sagar
